Package: AdmixtureTools
Type: Package
Title: AdmixtureTools allows to easily plot Admixture results and and modify the colours  
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mario Barbato
Maintainer: The package maintainer <mario_barbato@hotmail.com>
Description: With AdmixtureTools you can plot Admixture results, modify the order of the populations,
    define a new palette of colors and change how the colours are assigned to different clusters at 
    different K, just by clicking on the colours yo uwant to swap.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: 
    data.table, RColorBrewer
